  "title": "Technical Sales Manager (Crewing)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Overview</strong><br />The Technical Sales Manager will drive sales and solutioning for <strong>crewing-focused maritime ERP software</strong>, working closely with shipowners and ship managers. This role requires strong hands-on crewing knowledge and the ability to translate operational needs into effective software solutions.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lead sales and business development for crewing software solutions</p></li><li><p>Engage shipowners, ship managers, and crewing teams to understand operational workflows and pain points</p></li><li><p>Deliver product demonstrations, technical presentations, and solution proposals</p></li><li><p>Act as a subject-matter expert on crewing processes (planning, certification, payroll, compliance, rotation, reporting)</p></li><li><p>Support pre-sales and post-sales discussions alongside product and implementation teams</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong client relationships across the region</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Several years of hands-on experience in <strong>maritime crewing operations</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong understanding of end-to-end crewing processes and compliance requirements</p></li><li><p>Experience in a customer-facing, sales, or commercial role preferred</p></li><li><p>Able to explain technical solutions in a clear, practical manner</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working with software/ERP solutions in a maritime environment</p></li></ul>",
